WHERE h.position_ratio < 86 AND ( s.stock.name == "数资" OR s.stock.name == "技公" ) AND s.stock.name == "数资技公股" 
RETURN s.stock.name,n.name
LIMIT 50

MATCH (s:stock)<-[h:hold]-(pof:public_offering_fund)
WHERE ( s.stock.name == "数资" OR s.stock.name == "技公" ) AND s.stock.name == "数资技公股" AND h.position_ratio < 86 
RETURN s.stock.name,n.name
LIMIT 50
